{
  "stem": "19895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But as people were herded up that location-- because there were no places in the courtyard to take that many people anymore-- these tops of the tubes were kicked off, and sparks were coming.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were afraid of fire and overcrowdedness and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were staying there for two, three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then another location we were herded to, which was the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "16, 16.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why I was taken away at 16.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know what, this period of time from the racetrack to this period of time is about a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That comes later, in a couple of days later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This will be probably the third day of that, around Budapest situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we arrived to that other location, which is the champagne factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Torley Champagne Company had a factory, which was another concentration area for a lot of Jews of-- who were rounded up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, again, no food, minimal food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father sneaked away to try for money, to buy some foods from some neighboring location.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went into a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in a total fear that if he ever returns or they-- anybody who leaves the perimeter was shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And father came back with a bottle of milk and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and he had it under his coat, hidden, that he didn't have to give it away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because people were hungry, not only us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So in a corner, we were drinking milk with my father and bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- the two of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and it was starvation already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then people were starting to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were then divided into units, just like military.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one experience, which is very vivid in my memory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people escaped from our group.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
